Description: Timeless appeal. Effortless style. Everyday versatility. For over 50 years and counting, adidas Stan Smith Shoes have continued to hold their place as an icon. This pair shows off a fresh redesign as part of adidas' commitment to use only recycled polyester by 2024. With a vegan upper and an outsole made from rubber waste, they still have iconic style, they're just made with the planet in mind. This product is made with vegan alternatives to animal-derived ingredients or materials. It is also made with Primegreen, a series of high-performance recycled materials. 50% of upper is recycled content. No virgin polyester.

Get after the day in total comfort in these ultra-cushioned shoes. Inspired by the digital and tactile satisfaction of our everyday. Reflective pops define the tech upper of the ZX 2K BOOST 2.0. Lace in, let the softness embrace your feet. The cushioning of wrapped Boost brings satisfaction to every step.

Modern pants that make simplicity a statement. It's not just what you wear, it's how you wear it. Good thing these adidas twill pants are cut to move. Slip into the relaxed build and let your natural confidence shine. If the day calls for casual comfort or elevated style? You found both. This product is made with recycled content as part of our ambition to end plastic waste.

Swim with turtles or just lounge by the pool in legit adidas style. Make a statement without saying a word with tricolor Trefoils on the sides of these swim shorts. They're made of recycled nylon, part of adidas' efforts to help end plastic waste. Nothing but win.

A good hat can put the finishing touch on an outfit or casually cover up a bad hair day. And this adidas Bucket Hat is most definitely a good hat. The comfy cotton towel fabric and soft fringe edges give it a relaxed vibe no matter how you style it.
A parka made with lightweight, durable water-repellent fabric. Easily packs into an interior pocket for easy carrying.
Casual above-the-knee chino shorts with a sleek and breezy feel. We achieved the unique texture by slightly raising the high-density cotton twill and through a special dyeing and washing process.
Part of a collection of progressive essentials created in our Paris atelier by artistic director Christophe Lemaire and a team of international designers.
Designed with athletes in mind for stress-free performance. With DRY technology and cooling features. Made with 75% recycled polyester.
Our wrinkle-resistant shirt is so advanced it had to be specially engineered! Updated wrinkle-resistant processing holds up even after washing for easy care.

Inspired by the original that debuted in 1985, the Air Jordan 1 Low offers a clean, classic look that's familiar yet always fresh. It's made for casual mode, with an iconic design that goes with everything and never goes out of style.

Your workhorse with wings returns.The Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 38 continues to put a spring in your step, using the same responsive foam as its predecessor.Breathable mesh in the upper combines the comfort and durability you want with a wider fit at the toes.

The FFF Jacket is a lightweight, water-resistant layer that helps you stay dry, whether you're rushing on the pitch or on your commute. The mesh lining and vent let you stay airy and cool when you're on the move.

The Nike Sportswear t-shirt rethinks a layering staple. This woven cotton blend is lined with mesh for a cool, comfortable feel.Design details such as a snap shoulder placket and elastic cuffs and hem ensure this comfy top will remain a go-to layer for many seasons to come.
The Nike Therma-FIT Hoodie combines the playability and warmth of Nike's performance fleece with a loose and roomy fit. It's got 'NIKE' cut into large letters and stitched across the front.
